Over the last couple of years Dell has spent its time as a private company =
pivoting from a PC-maker with an enterprise business to a full-stack enterp=
rise player that also sells PCs. The company is private, so no one knows ho=
w it's going, but signs seem positive. That business, though, like all ente=
